        <li> <img src="img/activities_1_thumb.jpg" alt="" class="img-circle styled">
          <h4>Take a ride on Elephants</h4>
          <p> The adventure tour in India is popular and especially the elephant safari trips. Elephant safari helps the visitor to travel through such difficult terrains where even jeeps cannot venture.  <a href="more-wayanad.html" class="link_normal">Read more</a> </p>
        </li>
        <li><img src="img/activities_2_thumb.jpg" alt="" class="img-circle styled">
          <h4>Discover typical Food </h4>
          <p> Usually Kerala food is hot and spicy. Several fresh spices are used while food preparation that gives a unique aroma and flavor to the food. <a href="more-wayanad.html" class="link_normal">Read more</a> </p>
        </li>
        <li><img src="img/activities_3_thumb.jpg" alt="" class="img-circle styled">
          <h4>Learn to cook deliciuos food</h4>
          <p> The best part of travelling across Kerala is that one never has to eat the same typical food everywhere. You can tantalise your taste buds in every region in Kerala as every district has its own mouth-watering sumptuous delicacies which must not be missed at any cost<a href="more-wayanad.html" class="link_normal">Read more</a> </p>
        </li>
        <li><img src="img/activities_4_thumb.jpg" alt="" class="img-circle styled">
          <h4>Ayurvedic Treatments</h4>
          <p> The name of Kerala is famous for many attractions such as artistic temples, placid backwaters and panoramic hill stations. Perhaps, the ayurvedic treatment available in Kerala is peculiar to the tradition and heritage of Kerala. <a href="more-wayanad.html" class="link_normal">Read more</a> </p>
        </li>
