        <p> Kerala is one of the most charming and captivating states of India. Situated alongside the azure Arabian Sea, it is one of the most sought after tourism and holiday destinations in the country. It is noted for its natural beauty created by beaches, backwaters, hill stations, wildlife, etc. Also known as God's Own Country, Kerala tourism also features some historical and religious monuments. It attracts travelers and tourists from all over the world. </p>
